     C                     MOVE ZHTNI     G7HTNI
     C                     MOVE ZMCOD     G7MCOD
     C                     MOVE ZMMEI     G7MMEI
     C                     END
     C                     END
     C/SPACE 1
     C           STEP03    TAG
     C                     EXFMTGBFPW212
     C                     SETOF                     949596
     C                     SETOF                     9997
     C/SPACE 1
     C           *INKC     IFEQ '1'
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    MENT
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    G7MEK1
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    G7MEK2
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    G7MEK3
     C                     Z-ADD0         G7SAIZ
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    XTOKU
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    XNKOJ
     C                     GOTO STEP01
     C                     END
     C/SPACE 1
     C           G7HTNK    IFEQ 0
     C                     SETON                     9994
     C                     MOVE ER,12     MSG
     C                     GOTO STEP03
     C                     END
     C/SPACE 1
     C           G7HTNI    IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     SETON                     9995
     C                     MOVE ER,13     MSG
     C                     GOTO STEP03
     C                     END
     C/SPACE 1
     C           G7HTNI    IFNE 'K'
     C           G7HTNI    IFNE 'C'
     C                     SETON                     9995
     C                     MOVE ER,14     MSG
     C                     GOTO STEP03
     C                     END
     C                     END
     C/SPACE 1
     C*******>>  UTOKU     IFEQ 3174
     C*******>>  G7MCOD    IFEQ *BLANK
     C*******>>            SETON                     9996
     C*******>>            MOVE ER,15     MSG
     C*******>>            GOTO STEP03
     C*******>>            END
     C*******>>            END
     C/SPACE 1
     C           G7MMEI    IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     SETON                     9997
     C                     MOVE ER,16     MSG
     C                     GOTO STEP03
     C                     END
     C/SPACE 1
     C           *INKE     CABEQ'0'       STEP03
     C                     MOVE *DATE     KHIZK
     C                     MOVE PUS       G7KOME
     C                     TIME           WTIME
     C           MENT      IFEQ '0'
     C                     MOVE 'D'       G7SKJY
     C                     MOVE *DATE     SHIZK
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    G7SKJY
     C                     Z-ADD0         SHIZK
     C                     END
     C           MENT      IFEQ '2'
     C                     MOVE UTOKU     G7TOKU
     C                     MOVE PTKOJ     G7TKOJ
     C                     END
     C/SPACE 1
     C           *IN05     IFEQ '1'
     C                     WRITEGBFPL211
     C                     ELSE
     C                     UPDATGBFPL211
     C                     END
     C/SPACE 1
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    MENT
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    G7MEK1
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    G7MEK2
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    G7MEK3
     C                     Z-ADD0         G7SAIZ
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    XTOKU
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    XNKOJ
     C                     GOTO STEP01
     C/SPACE 1
     C           END       TAG
     C                     SETON                     LR
**
E-01 UPDATE INST IS ERROR <0= CANCEL. 1= CHANGE. 2= ADD>
E-02 SURFACE TREATMENT CODE IS NOT INPUT
E-03 SURFACE TREATMENT CODE IS * THAN NOT INPUT
E-04 SURFACE TREATMENT COATING THICKNESS IS NOT INPUT
E-05 NOT INPUT THAT SURFACE TREATMENT COATING THICKNESS IS *
E-06 SIZE IS NOT INPUT
E-07 CANCEL WAS APPOINTED, BUT M/F IS CANCELLED ALREADY
E-08 CANCEL WAS APPOINTED, BUT M/F DOES NOT EXIST
E-09 A CHANGE WAS APPOINTED, BUT M/F IS CANCELLED ALREADY
E-10 A CHANGE WAS APPOINTED, BUT M/F DOES NOT EXIST
E-11 ADD WAS APPOINTED, BUT M/F EXISTS
E-12 SURFACE TREATMENT UNIT PRICE IS NOT INPUT
E-13 UNIT OF SURFACE TREATMENT UNIT PRICE IS NOT INPUT
E-14 INSTRUCTION OF UNIT IS ERROR <K = KG. C = COUNT>
E-15 CUSTOMER SURFACE TREATMENT CODE IS NOT INPUT
E-16 A NAME OF SURFACE TREATMENT IS NOT INPUT
E-17 SURFACE TREATMENT SPECIAL CODE IS NOT INPUT
E-18 SURFACE TREATMENT SPECIAL CODE IS NOT RIGHT
E-19 UPD INST- CAN NOT INPUT COPIED CUSTOMER EXCEPT ADDTION.
E-20 UPD INST- CAN NOT INPUT COPIED FACTORY EXCEPT ADDTION.
